==English==

==={{acronym}}=== 
'''OBP'''

#{{baseball}} The baseball statistic of "On-Base Percentage" that reports the ratio of the hits plus walks divided by the official at-bats plus walks.  It is usually reported as a ratio and not a percentage despite its name and is thought to more closely correlate to a players true value than the batting average.

